      "location": "auth",
      "position": "after",
      "content": "The Arcade Web MCP Server uses [Firecrawl](https://www.firecrawl.dev/) to scrape, crawl, and map websites.\n\n**Global Environment Variables:**\n- `FIRECRAWL_API_KEY`: Your [Firecrawl](https://www.firecrawl.dev/) API key.\n\n<Callout type=\"warning\">\n**Keep the API key secret** â€” do not commit `FIRECRAWL_API_KEY` to source control or expose it in client-side code.\n</Callout>\n\n<Callout type=\"info\">\nCheck [Firecrawl](https://www.firecrawl.dev/) for available deployment and enterprise options (cloud, self-hosted, enterprise plans) and follow their configuration guides for API access.\n</Callout>",
      "header": "## Auth"
    }
